{"tid":1049824,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"終於有方法輕輕鬆鬆月入十二萬","createTime":"2019-03-06T14:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T17:18:34.000Z","uid":12987,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35ab128595518bd53b0736105bcc797889dd5cc2","tid":1049824,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSax3s2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSax3s2.png&h=ed76916b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果每日去旺角垃圾筒執珍珠奶茶個杯<br />\n一日執100個<br />\n$10 x 100個 = $1000<br />\n30日 x $1000 = $30,000<br />\n<br />\n我用$5000月薪分別請4個流浪漢幫我執膠杯<br />\n呢度月入$120,000 扣除成本$20,000<br />\n都仲賺緊$100,000<br />\n<br />\n加埋自己去執再加$30,000<br />\n最後請多個姐姐洗杯月薪$10,000<br />\n<br />\n到時月入$120,000 唔洗交稅<br />\n幾個月已經夠比首期<br />\n到時再上市集資 收息都夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f096a8b327682ee0e508c261fd553ab6dc7270","tid":1049824,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6c1846c3b331075c4fb1f6191b0407ef598dcb2","tid":1049824,"uid":65178,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"你覺得好好笑？"},{"pid":"9ef3b2d46d24e6b59ffeeac1e2f0d99a2e070460","tid":1049824,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"你不如話有5千萬本齋收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4815a80c9fd7d1ed60699ef1547a74b6cd7eea8e","tid":1049824,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"咁煩架，all in 今年利物浦拎英超就夠啦，包上買車兼買樓"},{"pid":"d2fafcab84c95b5a3033246a4469d51fc842a425","tid":1049824,"uid":12987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06f096a8b327682ee0e508c261fd553ab6dc7270","tid":1049824,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cite